Written by Jiayi Wang 2025.5
This is a directory to run particle number vs chemical potential for a specific subunit. Modify the for loop in run.sh to sample different chemical potentials. 

mu_coeff.txt and pair_coeff_commands.txt are chemical potential and interaction energies input file, already written in lammps input format to be included in the lammps input file. 

in.xlms_toy.bak: lammps input file

traj, Snumber and lammps_log are directories to collect results. 
